---
source: tests/lifecycle_tests/clause.rs
expression: snapshot
---
$ govctl rfc new Deprecate Twice RFC
Created RFC: gov/rfc/RFC-0001/rfc.toml
  Clauses dir: gov/rfc/RFC-0001/clauses
exit: 0

$ govctl clause new RFC-0001:C-ONE Clause One -s Specification -k normative
Created clause: gov/rfc/RFC-0001/clauses/C-ONE.toml
  Added to section 'Specification', path: clauses/C-ONE.toml
exit: 0

$ govctl clause deprecate RFC-0001:C-ONE --force
Deprecated clause: RFC-0001:C-ONE
exit: 0

$ govctl clause deprecate RFC-0001:C-ONE --force
error[E0208]: Clause is already deprecated. Valid transition from deprecated: superseded via `clause supersede` (RFC-0001:C-ONE)
exit: 1
